---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Articles
description: Long-form writing on operations, platforms, and the AI features that matter.
permalink: /articles/
---

<div class="container">
  <h1>Articles</h1>
  <p class="muted">Longer-form thinking on operations, platforms, and the AI features worth building.</p>

  {% if collections.articles.length > 0 %}
    <ul class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.articles %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
            <p class="muted small">{{ post.date | date }}</p>
            {% if post.data.summary %}<p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% else %}
    <p class="muted">No articles published yet.</p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
